</div>

<div class="row">
	<div class="col-md-6">
		<%= image_tag 'tbmm.png', alt: 'The Beard Maketh the Man', class: 'portfolio-image img-responsive img-rounded' %>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-6">
		<h3 class="portfolio-title">The Beard Maketh the Man</h3>
		<h4>TBMM is an application to help users find beard grooming products with the Etsy api. Built with Sinatra and vanilla JavaScript.</h4>
